dcterms:description: MUTAG is a dataset consisting of chemical compounds represented by graphs. The task is to predict whether the chemical compound is mutagenic.
dcterms:title: MUTAG

dcterms:description: Proteins is a dataset consisting of proteins represented by graphs. The objective is to predict whether a protein functions as an enzyme.
dcterms:title: Proteins

dcterms:creator: P. Yanardag
S. Vishwanathan
dcterms:description: IMDB-Binary is a set of graphs corresponding to ego-networks of actors and actresses. An edge is drawn between two actors if they were cast in the same movie. The task is to predict whether a movie is romance or action.
dcterms:title: IMDB-Binary

dcterms:creator: P. Yanardag
S. Vishwanathan
dcterms:description: Reddit-Binary consists of graphs corresponding to online discussion threads. An edge is drawn between two users if one has replied to the other. The task is to predict whether a thread belongs to a discussion forum or a question answering forum.
dcterms:title: Reddit-Binary
